title: Open Weekends For Tour - Renovated - Luxury Amenities - Great Location
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Studio+ Highlighting Wellbeats!', 'Offering a Variety of On-Demand Exercise Programs', '-Resident Portal: Enter Maintenance Requests Online when Convenient', '-Over 20,000 Sq Ft of Amenities!', '-Extra stuff?', 'Convenient Storage Lockers Available', '-Engineered wood plank flooring throughout', '-Package Concierge Offering 24-Hour Access to Packages', '-Payments', 'Accepted: Credit Card, Cash via MoneyGram, Apple Pay and FREE E-Check', '-Controlled Access to Building Towers', '-Professional, Friendly Office and Maintenance Staff', '-Walk in showers in select two and three bedroom apartments', '-Large, private balcony with panoramic views', '-The Cinema Offers Cozy Seating for Private Viewing Parties', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
